{{infobox company | name = Nutaku | logo = File:Nutaku logo.svg | logo_caption = Nutaku's 2018 logo, neutral colored. | founded = January 2015 | location = {{hlist|[[Montreal]]|[[Quebec]]|[[Canada]]}} | industry = Adult | products = {{hlist|PC Games|Online games|Free-to-play games|Downloadable games|Mobile games}} | website = {{ubl|{{url|nutaku.com}}|{{url|nutaku.net}}}} | owner = [[MindGeek]] }}
'''Nutaku''' is an adult gaming platform with primarily hentai games. Located in Canada, Nutaku offers games with mature content. The platform focuses on browser games, downloadable and mobile games<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.mmorpg.com/newsroom.cfm?loadNews=36994/Nutaku-Portal-EN-Versions-of-Great-Online-Games-Incoming|title = Nutaku Portal - EN Versions of Great Online Games Incoming]]|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = |first = }}</ref> both free with [[microtransactions]] and purchasable. Nutaku has 100 million visitors per month<ref>https://www.destructoid.com/nutaku-and-i-get-busy-talking-about-sex-games-417447.phtml</ref> and provides a platform for western [[Independent video game development|indie]] web game developers. Nutaku offers pornographic games of various genres including [[action-adventure]], [[massively multiplayer online game]], [[real-time strategy]], [[tower defense]], [[dating sim]], [[clicker]], [[collectible card game]], [[puzzle]], [[turn-based strategy]] (TBS), strategy, visual novels, kinetic novels, and [[virtual reality]].
==History== In December 2014, [[Hokuto_Corporation#DMM | DMM]] partnered with Nutaku with the objective of marketing and publishing games to the western market.<ref>http://www.dmm.co.jp/en/netgame/foreign/</ref> Nutaku is currently the sole distributor of DMM games outside Japan.
In January 2015, the platform was launched with four Japanese games that were translated for an English-speaking audience. Although they began with the release of card battle RPG “Lord of Valkyrie,” Nutaku has rapidly expanded its selection to include online games of the card-battle, adventure,<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.siliconera.com/2015/11/08/turn-based-jrpg-kanpani-girls-now-available-in-english/|title = Turn-Based JRPG Kanpani Girls Now Available In English|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = |first = }}</ref> city building,<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.develop-online.net/press-releases/clash-of-clans-meets-hentai-rpg-in-nutaku-rsquo-s-lsquo-girls-kingdom-rsquo/0212428/|title = Clash of Clans Meets Hentai RPG in Nutaku's 'Girls Kingdom'|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = |first = }}</ref> and sim genres.<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.lewdgamer.com/2015/08/11/everlasting-summer-shows-up-on-nutaku/|title = Adult Version of Everlasting Summer Shows up on Nutaku|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = |first = }}</ref> It is particularly noted for its broad selection of translated Japanese [[erotic game]]s.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hernandez|first1=Patricia|title=The People Who Translate Japanese Sex Games For Millions of Horny Fans|url=http://kotaku.com/the-people-who-translate-japanese-sex-games-for-million-1794000788|accessdate=April 5, 2017|work=Kotaku}}</ref>
In August 2015 an online version of [[Everlasting Summer]] with restored adult content was released on Nutaku.<ref>https://www.lewdgamer.com/2015/08/11/everlasting-summer-shows-up-on-nutaku/</ref> In November 2015 Nutaku announced the launch of an all-ages website.<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://mmos.com/news/nutaku-launches-new-all-ages-gaming-portal-featuring-kanpani-girls |title = Nutaku Launches New All-Ages Gaming Portal Featuring Kanpani Girls|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = |first = }}</ref>
In July 2016, Nutaku announced their partnership with Kimochi, a downloadable game client focused on the digital distribution of adult games from around the world.<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.pcgamesn.com/sex-games-investment |title = An adult entertainment website is about to insert $2 million into sex games|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = |first = }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://motherboard.vice.com/read/steam-sex-games |title = Nutaku Is Building the Steam of Hentai Sex Games|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = |first = }}</ref> In early 2017, Nutaku released [[Android (operating system)|Android]] compatible version of some of their more popular games.
In February 2017, Nutaku announced the launch of Kimochi Red Light, a new crowdfunding platform that's been set up exclusively to crowdfund adult games.<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.kotaku.co.uk/2017/02/09/theres-a-new-crowdfunding-site-exclusively-for-18-games|title = There's a Crowdfunding Site Exclusively for 18+ Games|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = |first = }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = https://venturebeat.com/2017/02/07/nutaku-launches-kimochi-red-light-to-crowdfund-adult-games/|title = Nutaku launches Kimochi Red Light to crowdfund adult games|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = |first = }}</ref>
At Anime Expo 2017 (July), Nutaku held a panel in which an employee, expressed the platform as being "the steamy [[Steam (software)|Steam]]". By this time, the platform had reached 9 million users.
